+## [0.2.1] - 2026-05-27
+
+Documentation-only release. No runtime, dependency, or API changes — under `0.x`,
+non-breaking changes increment the patch version.
+
+### Added
+
+- **ADR-0001** documenting the test-harness and pure-logic coverage strategy
+  (`docs/adr/ADR-0001-test-harness-and-pure-logic-coverage.md`).
+- **Backlog brainstorm** captured in both Markdown and JSON
+  (`docs/backlog-brainstorm.md`, `docs/backlog-brainstorm.json`).
+- **Moonshots planning set** under `docs/harness/moonshots-2026-05-21/`
+  (`INDEX.md`, `moonshots.md`).
+
+### Changed
+
+- **README** tech-stack section refreshed to reflect the 0.2.0 platform
+  (Next.js 16 · React 19 · TypeScript 6 · Tailwind CSS 4 · ESLint 10).
